00:06:10.639 --> 00:06:19.039
So let's talk about how we can uh

00:06:14.639 --> 00:06:21.840
determine or estimate W's that can do

00:06:19.039 --> 00:06:24.400
well on some loss functions that we we

00:06:21.840 --> 00:06:27.600
want for this specific linear case. We

00:06:24.400 --> 00:06:32.639
need to basically say what is not a good

00:06:27.600 --> 00:06:36.000
