So going back to what we did here.

00:10:44.640 --> 00:10:51.200
So basically what we are doing we are

00:10:47.440 --> 00:10:56.000
minimizing the distance between our y

00:10:51.200 --> 00:10:59.760
and our prediction using the model. So

00:10:56.000 --> 00:11:03.120
if I want to give u a geometric

